{"tid":2403132,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"儂友和你散貨 場內搵「初心」","createTime":"2021-02-11T02:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T11:05:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d070f9c5863eb4157ef801ea7ce684ed9e547109","tid":2403132,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:22:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/XCAQC22AEBEVDG5QMHGJL6ZQUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FXCAQC22AEBEVDG5QMHGJL6ZQUE%2F&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=bf73d1d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FXCAQC22AEBEVDG5QMHGJL6ZQUE%2F&h=1c480648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/XCAQC22AEBEVDG5QMHGJL6ZQUE/</a><br />\n<br />\n儂友和你散貨 場內搵「初心」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CDIfZEtzfhOrFGPbXGXg7jC5Z9I=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3M5DEWRJJNFNLOJEIAONSGG65Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCDIfZEtzfhOrFGPbXGXg7jC5Z9I%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3M5DEWRJJNFNLOJEIAONSGG65Y.jpg&h=505222d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■儂友散貨場設簡單佈置，甫進門有連儂牆。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】曾遭食環署打壓的連儂說展覽捲土重來，邀逾40獨立品牌在旺角廣東道樓上舖舉辦小型「散貨場」。策劃人表示，即使屢遭阻攔，始終想借不同形式的活動找回大眾自6.12時的初心。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黃色年宵旺場 今最後衝刺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩成營利捐運動支援組織<br />\n<br />\n去年12月，由一同建構連儂牆而認識的自發團體「儂友」、一同籌劃「連儂說展覽」暨聖誕市集，惟遭食環以限聚為由禁止舉辦展覽，活動僅容以市集形式完成。當時只負責出橋的策劃人「肥貓主人」表示，「好可惜我當時唔喺現場，我仲坐緊監」，形容在牆內聽聞消息深感難受。但「打壓咁犀利唔通就咩都唔搞咩」，她指仍想憑着初心，將活動以不同形式呈現，喚起大眾如6.12時的初心。<br />\n<br />\n與連儂說展覽一樣，今次名為和你跨年的散貨場活動，僅限商業買賣，借用樓上舖「梘單製皂」場地，擺滿16小攤檔，售賣逾40獨立品牌產品。場內設有簡單佈置，甫進門有連儂牆，小攤位有能敲出《榮光》樂聲的小水瓶。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黃大仙祠直播 法師代上頭炷香<br />\n<br />\n參展攤檔「捐L晒」售賣書籍、食品和手作，檔主S小姐形容品牌過往是血汗工廠，五名有份合作的人士均是抽公餘時間手製產品，然後全數不計成本捐予協助抗爭者機構。然而生活越來越難捱，能抽空製作產品的時間太少，令攤檔差點無法維持經營。<br />\n<br />\n和你跨年活動地點為廣東道1143 號協和工業大廈4樓，即日開始，除大年初一外，舉行五日直至年初四，免費入場，攤檔將會把兩成營利直接捐予運動支援組織。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mXrhhbZrUlHylM3Wba4bMchL_Lo=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VTIRFB2GINFVNKGQ43B5CCZHKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmXrhhbZrUlHylM3Wba4bMchL_Lo%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVTIRFB2GINFVNKGQ43B5CCZHKY.jpg&h=c7901e61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■小攤位的小水瓶能敲出《榮光》樂聲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DQxCJXYqsd6csg6sfjg1reLIpYw=/998x450/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U6SL3JHW7RCH7HSIZJKA52L7B4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDQxCJXYqsd6csg6sfjg1reLIpYw%3D%2F998x450%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU6SL3JHW7RCH7HSIZJKA52L7B4.gif&h=717e56de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■場內有黃氣逼人的賀年飾物，亦有以《蘋果》A1製作的掛飾。"},{"pid":"15faf149fe615442e57a237fdf46222fbd75a160","tid":2403132,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:23:04.000Z","msg":"課金課金課金 入錢入錢入錢！！"},{"pid":"ba7f041831d6a44e00244d6d007229c390afe24b","tid":2403132,"uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T02:24:01.000Z","msg":"#2五毛即到"},{"pid":"845c0d7aedb951799111a0537b15c226cb79bd7a","tid":2403132,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2db0e46c5eaf5ae05c12ebd6501d55518c8cd21","tid":2403132,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba7f041831d6a44e00244d6d007229c390afe24b","tid":